    <item>
      <title>贝莱德（Blackrock），投资者将资金用于挣扎的聚合器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/blackrock-investors-pump-funds-into-struggling-aggregator-razor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，包括贝莱德公司（Blackrock Inc.）在内的投资者已同意向剃刀集团提供至少1500万美元的贷款，因为德国电子商务品牌聚合商试图避免流动性紧缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/blackrock-investors-pump-funds-into-struggling-aggregator-razor</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 10:05:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富有货的迈图安（Meituan）希望建立在香港胜利的基础上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/deep-pocketed-meituan-looks-to-build-on-its-hong-kong-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港居民西蒙·米奥（Simon Miao）在大流行期间签署了与弗洛尔（Driveroo）的食品交付订阅，但后来他取消了这笔款项，因为每月费用为98港元（12.61美元），并没有带来很多好处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/deep-pocketed-meituan-looks-to-build-on-its-hong-kong-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 10:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Openai要求白宫免除国家AI规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/openai-asks-white-house-for-relief-from-state-ai-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Openai已要求特朗普政府通过自愿与联邦政府自愿分享其模型，帮助屏蔽人工智能公司越来越多的拟议州法规。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/openai-asks-white-house-for-relief-from-state-ai-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在特朗普关税担忧的情况下，通用汽车韩国联盟领导人前往美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/gm-korea-union-leaders-head-to-the-us-amid-trump-tariff-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国通用汽车公司工厂的工会工人对唐纳德·特朗普总统的签约关税表示担忧，担心如果他们在工作的工厂（将成千上万的汽车运到美国）可能会失业，并以某种方式受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/gm-korea-union-leaders-head-to-the-us-amid-trump-tariff-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 08:53:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
