    <item>
      <title>日产的领导力雷吉格（Rejig）使外部董事吸引愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/nissan-leadership-rejig-that-keeps-external-directors-draws-ire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司（Nissan Motor Co.）的领导层改组不足以提出批评，促使一些人想知道，陷入困境的日本汽车制造商对解决财务状况并确保将确保其未来稳定的合作伙伴有多认真。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/nissan-leadership-rejig-that-keeps-external-directors-draws-ire</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 07:45:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔分享在命名芯片行业的老将谭（Tan）担任首席执行官之后跳跃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/intel-names-chip-industry-veteran-lip-bu-tan-as-its-next-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司（Intel Corp.）股票在周四的上市交易中跃升了约10％，因为它将Lip-Bu Tan任命为下一任首席执行官，并委托一名前董事会成员和半导体老兵拥有芯片行业中最艰难的工作之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/intel-names-chip-industry-veteran-lip-bu-tan-as-its-next-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 20:22:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
